Luka: Yes, it was... Just thinking about what everyone was feeling... Oh, I think I'm tearing up...
Miku: But An and the others... They didn't back down. They don't want to disappoint Nagi.
Miku: Which means we have to keep giving them all the support we can.
Miku: Rin, thank you for coming to get us. Also, we'll need to apologize to An and the others for eavesdropping.
Miku: And no more crying, you two. An and the others just made a big decision to stay on the path they chose.
Miku: So, let's keep doing our best for them!
Rin: Yeah!
